msgstr "/zork/, 名詞"

#: ../../Z/Zork.rst:9
msgid ""
"The second of the great early experiments in computer fantasy gaming; see "
":ref:`ADVENT`\\. Originally written on MIT-DM during 1977-1979, later "
"distributed with BSD Unix (as a patched, sourceless RT-11 FORTRAN binary; "
"see :ref:`retrocomputing`\\) and commercialized as ‘The Zork Trilogy’ by "
":ref:`Infocom`\\. The FORTRAN source was later rewritten for portability and"
" released to Usenet under the name \"Dungeon\". Both FORTRAN \"Dungeon\" and"
" translated C versions are available at many FTP sites; the commercial Zork "
"trilogy is available at `http://www.ifarchive.org/ "
"<http://www.ifarchive.org/>`_. See also :ref:`grue`\\. You can play Zork via"
" a `Java Applet <http://www.forkexec.com/html/play-zork1.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"コンピュータファンタジーゲームの偉大な初期の実験のうち2番目のもの。\\ :ref:`ADVENT`\\ を参照。元々は1977-1979年にMIT-"
"DM上で書かれ、後にBSD Unixとともに(パッチが当てられ、ソースのないRT-11 FORTRANバイナリとして。\\ "
":ref:`retrocomputing`\\ を参照)配布され、\\ :ref:`Infocom`\\ によって‘The Zork "
"Trilogy’として商品化された。FORTRANのソースは後に移植性のために書き直され、\"Dungeon\"という名でUsenetに公開された。FORTRAN版\"Dungeon\"と翻訳されたC版は、多くのFTPサイトで入手できる。商用のZorkトリロジーは\\"
" `http://www.ifarchive.org/ <http://www.ifarchive.org/>`_\\ で入手できる。\\ "
":ref:`grue`\\ も参照。\\ `Java Applet <http://www.forkexec.com/html/play-"
"zork1.html>`_\\ を通じてZorkを遊ぶこともできる。"
